{"tid":1299901,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"環保吸管使用注意！英女跌倒 金屬吸管插腦身亡","createTime":"2019-07-09T07:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T08:29:09.000Z","uid":150609,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5137e2e74722782c2b3835f82cb1f5ab09441231","tid":1299901,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtd5Y8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmtd5Y8B.jpg&h=ddede749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國一名女退休騎師，就因為摔倒，金屬吸管不小心穿透眼睛並插到大腦而死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n根據《都市日報》報導，英國多塞特郡（Dorset）一名60歲退休騎師埃琳娜（Elena<br />\nStruthers-Gardner）日前被發現倒臥在家中，一隻不鏽鋼吸管插在她的頭上。當時她拿<br />\n著裝有飲料的梅森罐，罐子旋上了杯蓋，杯蓋上並且有一個洞來固定這支不鏽鋼吸管。當<br />\n她正要走緊廚房時，不慎摔倒，接著不鏽鋼吸管刺穿她的左眼窩，並插入大腦。 <br />\n<br />\n「我沒有聽到她摔倒。」埃琳娜的伴侶曼蒂（Mandy Struthers-Gardner）表示她走到廚<br />\n房門口看到埃琳娜躺在書房和廚房之間的門口，並發出不尋常的咕嚕聲。曼蒂進一步表示<br />\n埃琳娜的梅森罐完好無缺的躺在地板上，「吸管也還插在罐子裡，但是吸管貼在她頭上。<br />\n」 <br />\n<br />\n埃琳娜隨即被送往普郡的南安普頓綜合醫院（Southampton General Hospital），然而由<br />\n於傷勢過重，第二天便去世了。 <br />\n<br />\n助理驗屍官布蘭登艾倫（Brendan Allen）表示沒有證據可以解釋埃琳娜是如何摔倒的，<br />\n但他補充道：「使用這些金屬吸管時，應該非常小心。」他表示這些金屬吸管不應與任何<br />\n形式的蓋子一起使用，「如果這個蓋子沒有被固定住，那麼吸管就會移開。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海龜沒死就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d348be9d8a40cb751522c3fb9d4329275571a5","tid":1299901,"uid":243516,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:59:04.000Z","msg":"最緊要海龜無事丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d075444ba7d351139c71bae1b41061a7c5eba4","tid":1299901,"uid":41368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:00:25.000Z","msg":"世界又少咗染污了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61216e3a6499413b73e3f65c0cd67d437910dd54","tid":1299901,"uid":184019,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:02:01.000Z","msg":"祝海龜一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac9987f649266964c3173ed7cc65706f5f6a360","tid":1299901,"uid":148076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:02:10.000Z","msg":"死神來了"},{"pid":"ea7686b0dedbb6f763044abd7bf4121fcac3bd90","tid":1299901,"uid":160404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:06:17.000Z","msg":"Happy tree friend?"},{"pid":"9d9fd803dc5732401ff31142a71a2be20778b945","tid":1299901,"uid":150609,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"龜龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fOkzSxV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfOkzSxV.jpg&h=7400506f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2aa531eca64c26e47d96285ad7894bf26a0eb2d0","tid":1299901,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8303337746e41e07d2418e4ca906f864566c3f5e","tid":1299901,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"驚唔驚去到60歲咁老"},{"pid":"337352627ff2c6b71533254d69d55542fd47e221","tid":1299901,"uid":18258,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"死多一個人，環保進程又邁進左一大步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16507703a2b16a865ded8baa7ff288b11aeae69","tid":1299901,"uid":194012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:17:58.000Z","msg":"wfc人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海龜冇事就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2ad769b614a5740f0ef0107c46de5950180ee0","tid":1299901,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:22:08.000Z","msg":"搞走塑班人講兩句"},{"pid":"b705767a8c017419b726d57b642da3c4332f6f76","tid":1299901,"uid":72085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:22:15.000Z","msg":"班環保撚上水未呀，好想聽你地解釋下，定係個別例子唔評論"},{"pid":"31c0fdc1c486488521f43d6c934c45de7143cee5","tid":1299901,"uid":265980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5137e2e74722782c2b3835f82cb1f5ab09441231","tid":1299901,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtd5Y8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmtd5Y8B.jpg&h=ddede749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國一名女退休騎師，就因為摔倒，金屬吸管不小心穿透眼睛並插到大腦而死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n根據《都市日報》報導，英國多塞特郡（Dorset）一名60歲退休騎師埃琳娜（Elena<br />\nStruthers-Gardner）日前被發現倒臥在家中，一隻不鏽鋼吸管插在她的頭上。當時她拿<br />\n著裝有飲料的梅森罐，罐子旋上了杯蓋，杯蓋上並且有一個洞來固定這支不鏽鋼吸管。當<br />\n她正要走緊廚房時，不慎摔倒，接著不鏽鋼吸管刺穿她的左眼窩，並插入大腦。 <br />\n<br />\n「我沒有聽到她摔倒。」埃琳娜的伴侶曼蒂（Mandy Struthers-Gardner）表示她走到廚<br />\n房門口看到埃琳娜躺在書房和廚房之間的門口，並發出不尋常的咕嚕聲。曼蒂進一步表示<br />\n埃琳娜的梅森罐完好無缺的躺在地板上，「吸管也還插在罐子裡，但是吸管貼在她頭上。<br />\n」 <br />\n<br />\n埃琳娜隨即被送往普郡的南安普頓綜合醫院（Southampton General Hospital），然而由<br />\n於傷勢過重，第二天便去世了。 <br />\n<br />\n助理驗屍官布蘭登艾倫（Brendan Allen）表示沒有證據可以解釋埃琳娜是如何摔倒的，<br />\n但他補充道：「使用這些金屬吸管時，應該非常小心。」他表示這些金屬吸管不應與任何<br />\n形式的蓋子一起使用，「如果這個蓋子沒有被固定住，那麼吸管就會移開。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海龜沒死就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:24:56.000Z","msg":"環保撚真麻煩"},{"pid":"65f8a5b6e592d11d5763f190e86844fb36099b9b","tid":1299901,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:26:31.000Z","msg":"gay婆加環保能 重唔係天譴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dffd88a574529d80a29dd0646a4568ed8b021f6","tid":1299901,"uid":133086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:29:09.000Z","msg":"膠飲管可能都要死 真係死神來了"}]}